description:
Here's the detailed installation video for the Squarewheels APEX Digital Dashboard for Infiniti Q50/Q60.  

Remove OEM Cluster
Perform Mileage Sync
Route HDMI & USB
Connect to MK7 (optional)
Finish the install

APEX Digital Dash Overview:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Iz7UOMplLDk

Available for purchase now at:
https://squarewheelsauto.com/products/apex-digital-dashboard-instrument-cluster-for-infiniti-q50-q60-2014-2024

APEX Installation Guide:
https://squarewheelsauto.com/blogs/videos/apex-digital-cluster-installation-guide
00:00 Introduction
00:45 RELAX. You're not gonna break anything
01:40 Removing the Q50/Q60 Dashboard
03:59 Sync your mileage to the APEX Digital Dash
08:19 Hook up the HDMI from your MK7 (bonus)

chapters.title: RELAX. You're not gonna break anything
Sync your mileage to the APEX Digital Dash
Hook up the HDMI from your MK7 (bonus)
